channel.desc: Debate 2003 The host presents extensive footage and commentary from the making of major Hollywood productions, highlighting what makes a blockbuster and what elements determine its success, in addition to introspective interviews with actors and filmmakers. Angela Valley, Michelle Blenker, Michael Keaton, Oscar Isaac, Anya Taylor-Joy, Keri Russell, Jason Momoa, David Freydt, Paul Wynne, Paul Wynne, Anya Taylor Joy, Janett Hermosillo, Ann-Marie Lariccia, Martin Saint Charles, Reginald de Guillebon.
